<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>If any object containing a Zend_Db_Adapter_Abstract object is serialised the database connection is destroyed forcing a reconnect.</p>

<p>This is caused by the _connection variable being set to false in __sleep. Simple solution is to remove that line. The __sleep return value is telling PHP not to serialise _connection anyway so it is redundant.</p>

